Name: FREAKOUT
About the game: Freakout is a 1-4 player online co-op survival horror game. Visit your school and find all your seized items and don't get caught by the possessed principal and his pet dog. Run, Scream, hide. Just don't get caught. 1-4 player online co-op Make use of our in-game positional voice chat. Bring friends, or find other players using the server browser. Single player Take your shot at visiting your school alone and find items by yourself! Proximity Voice Chat Nothing better than hearing your 'friends' scream in the distance Investigate Use your skills to find clues and collect items to investigate what happened in your school. Enraged Monster If you successfully released all the goats that are about to get sacrificed then the monstrous principal gets enraged. During this phase, he will be able to kill survivors. Play as a goat If you die as a survivor, you’ll reappear as a goat but you’ll still be able to help your friends escape by doing things such as; finding items for other players to use or distracting the monster. Challenging gameplay Every match you’ll play is going to be different. Your perks, escape points, roles and the item placement will all be randomized. You will always feel uneasy because there’s no way to predict how the game will go. Warning This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.
